# PROJECT CONTEXT & GLOBAL VARIABLES
# ⚠️ INSTRUCTION: Attach this file context to every prompt in this session.

[PROJECT IDENTITY]
Name: City Sheet
Type: Travel Directory & Utility Tool
Stack: Next.js 14+ (App Router), Supabase (Auth + DB), Tailwind CSS, Netlify.

[CORE PURPOSE]
A high-performance "cheat sheet" for travelers.
Key Feature ("The Hook"): A "Translation Bridge" that allows users to copy local text (e.g., Japanese/Thai) to the clipboard to show to taxi drivers or waiters.

[VISUAL IDENTITY (DETERMINISTIC)]
1. Colors (Tailwind):
   - Brand Primary: indigo-600 (Buttons, Links, Active States)
   - Background: slate-50 (App Shell)
   - Surface: white (Cards, Modals)
   - Local-Text Highlight: amber-50 (bg) + amber-900 (text) <--- CRITICAL for the Hook.
   - Text: slate-900 (Headings), slate-600 (Body).

2. Icons:
   - Library: lucide-react (Do not use Heroicons or FontAwesome).
   - Common: Copy, Check, MapPin, Search, Menu, Star, ThumbsUp, MessageSquare.

3. Typography:
   - Font: Inter (via next/font/google).
   - Base Size: 16px.

[PLACEHOLDERS & ASSETS]
- Images: Use "https://placehold.co/800x600/e2e8f0/475569?text=City+Image" for testing.
- Logo: Use text "CitySheet" in a <div> until SVG is provided.
- Mock Data:
   - City: Paris
   - Place: "Croissant Shop" (Local: クロワッサン)
   - Category: must-eat

[EXTERNAL KEYS (ENV placeholders)]
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000

[NON-GOALS (STRICT PROHIBITIONS)]
1. NO User Image Uploads (Curated images only).
2. NO Anonymous Comments (Login required via Supabase).
3. NO Infinite Scroll (Use "Load More" button).
4. NO Sticky Ads in middle of content (Only Footer/Sidebar).
5. NO Redux/Zustand (Use React Context/Local State).
